Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:08.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 'Oh' unecessary or not? I'm leaning towards yes; what do you think? - delamoo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:15.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:18.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:24.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:24.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:36.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened... to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:18.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:20.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:23.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that field of pampas grass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:42.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am holding her, but it's not what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:46.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I gave alcohol to an innocent girl and took her to a secluded place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:47.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:56.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Comment: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.70,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it enough, but I am very sorry.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:02.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alternative: "I deeply apologize for doing such a bad thing." Which is better?
Comment: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:02.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware of the situation, so I became a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that "a little upset"? You old maid.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:08.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TL HAAALP: Koi says Violent intimidator? Old maid sounds terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:10.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:16.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:16.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:16.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:18.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks familiar.
Comment: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Seems or looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand out much though.
Comment: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ALTERNATIVE: I don't leave a very strong\Nimpression on people. BetteR?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:29.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've met before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you've been here a few times for checkups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:37.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, lots of weird things really did happen on your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:40.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that just makes it all the more memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:44.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become friends with Kano, instead of just playing with me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you might get along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're both pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:51.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Comment: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:56.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ALTERNATIVE: "What's wrong?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to get my pay for today's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wait till tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:04.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be difficult if I try to pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's my-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gone to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:24.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeep!
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:24.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to turn on the lights so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:32.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:32.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't properly examine you in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Kano, you've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me in weird places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a proper clinical technique, called "palpation".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In examinations, you don't caress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:47.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I guess it was just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have any cats here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:56.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kano, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong, Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:07.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:14.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating the same words, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:22.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:22.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my only treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:24.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my precious little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Onee-chan hugging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came and hugged me, so I held you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:41.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to hurry up and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:46.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:46.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But can we stay like this for just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You held me like this when Daddy passed away, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:59.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you have a nice scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, a cicada flew in through the vent again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the soy sauce bottle fell over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the salad oil spilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:11.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, Yukito-san's bacon and eggs went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah-wah-wah-wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:23.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something happened to this food, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me as if, "wow, he's actually eating it!"?
Comment: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:46.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Clumsy line above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not looking like that, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't taste like cicadas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:12.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:19.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:19.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:19.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:19.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll see you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least do enough to earn your wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have something else for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to say something, just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But a pay raise is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's about last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.19,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've been looking for him for a while, but I can't seem to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:40.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato... Where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's starting to set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anywhere else to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you use your magic to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:12.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think my magic works like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was given this bandana,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:22.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to keep it on until I become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:22.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it off until then, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:25.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I take it off, I'll be able to use my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was little, so I don't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been wrapped around my wrist ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:37.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been troublesome at times, like during swimming and health checkups,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was even teased a few times too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, Onee-chan always saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:48.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I've been able to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come all the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could possibly be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito-kun, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized where Potato is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:03.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:05.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:07.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:11.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't ever make me worry like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yukito-kun, how did you know that he was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... well... uh... what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:33.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko Pikopik-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever wander off again without telling me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you did what you say.
Comment: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alternative (maybe better): You always say you will. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really not remember anything about what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:01.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:01.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, will you listen to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you can tell me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:17.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly remember anything about my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was never very healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She became sick right after she gave birth to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and passed away when I was about three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:31.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad would often say, "Your mom was like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:35.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I couldn't picture her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:39.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but, but it's not so bad; I wasn't that lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:43.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan was like a mom to me, and dad was always around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:57.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means that Onee-chan was without a mom for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently I realized how unfair that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:07.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was always busy with the clinic, and then he got sick himself from working too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I could do was watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:20.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:20.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan works and takes care of me, but I can't really do anything to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not much help either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:41.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would use it to meet my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her and apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:50.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank her, not apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother is the reason that you're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:01.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone said to me, "I'm sorry that you gave birth to me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mom, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:16.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, she went to the same place your mom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:27.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:33.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:33.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere beyond this sky is a girl with wings."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my mom's favorite saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for that girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:44.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then someday, when I can fly, I'll look for that girl for you.
Comment: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.82,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,KAMIO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't feeling very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:00.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were there, she wouldn't rest well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her mother so it shouldn't bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm her mother, we do have other issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you aren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't pick you up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:28.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:28.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're busy with other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like dinosaurs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she like dinosaurs so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:42.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:42.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always liked them, ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know anything about her, even though she's your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:50.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that it was her birthday yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:55.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does that girl act strangely during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she always strange?
Comment: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:57.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blah, note to self. Not the same as Ep2 preview
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if there's nothing, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, enough with this trivial talk; it's finally the main event of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The erotic confessions corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did we end up going there?!
Comment: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: above line feels clumsy, but it might just be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just saying the title turns me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:16.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a pervert or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:24.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, dinosaurs thrived for millions and millions of years, but then they faced their end and went extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad and makes me emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:44.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to describe it, but I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the scent of the wind, the feel of the breeze on my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:50.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the way the air moves and the passing of the seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:57.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:01.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where my dreams are taking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:09.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get hit by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.62,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's the 'suika wari' today, huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:12.37,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,TL NOTE: 'suika wari' is watermelon cracking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kano wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.17,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you spoiling her a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.63,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.27,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.71,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Set...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.14,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's impossible to make money here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.42,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't crash into me every single time!
Comment: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 'single' remove maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:49.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:49.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop always acting so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:56.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little busy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it, you will live here from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:16:59.98,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:16:59.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with didn't you want me to leave town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:35.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:40.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a wonderful special talent, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:44.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:44.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap clap clap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use a bit of what is called "magic".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:53.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many mysteries in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I have a special thank you gift.
Comment: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:56.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice Coupon\N1000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl with wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:11.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:16.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the same girl as my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a little girl, I had a picture book like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:34.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the picture book, there was a girl with pure white wings on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a little girl, I dreamt of flying through the sky with her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:45.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing strange about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:53.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if the purpose of your journey is to look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:59.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because everyone has a destination they want to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:07.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are going to be beautiful again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it well at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A destination, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with today's homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:28.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:30.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-A-R-D-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:38.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to play cards with you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Play by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, we have come from a faraway planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:56.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:56.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:05.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you two go that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, do you have any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:19.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to look anywhere we can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:19.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.77,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:28.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he asking us to follow him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.55,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she said she'd already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tighly clasping my only treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:43.56,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:43.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:47.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano.
Comment: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:40.98,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:45.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, I am writing this to you because I think you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:49.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally decided to go to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:53.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling it will make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:57.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that I will meet the girl you are looking for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:03.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long it will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:04.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will definitely bring her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:07.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you can help Onee-chan until I return.
Comment: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:10.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4